<!DOCTYPE html>

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head runat="server">
    <title></title>
</head>
<body>
    <p><strong>List of Users</strong></p>
<p>This screen will display the list of Users along with their basic details such as the Organization they belong to, their Email Address, Phone Number, Role and their current account status</p>

<p>Click on the Sort Icons to sort the list</p>

 <p>You can customize the list of items displayed on the page by selecting the value from the records per page dropdown list </p>

<p>You can search for an item from the list by typing the search keyword in the Search text box</p>

<p>Click on the Add New User button to add a new User</p>

<p>Click on any of the User Name to edit the particular user</p>

<p>You can naviage between the list by using the navigation / paging buttons below the list</p>
</body>
</html>
